{"type":"message","id":"2f81ae4f","parentId":"b26ef7ce","timestamp":"2026-03-09T05:21:30.039Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"\n\n# Your Job\n\nCreate a standalone HTML file at `public/react-app.html` that includes:\n1. A complete React component rendered via CDN (using React 18, ReactDOM 18, and Babel standalone)\n2. Tailwind CSS via CDN for styling\n3. A nice UI component - build a clean card-based layout with a header, interactive counter component, and a list of features\n4. The page should be responsive and visually polished with Tailwind utility classes\n5. Include proper meta tags for viewport scaling\n\nThe React component should demonstrate state management (useState) and include:\n- A modern hero section with gradient background\n- An interactive counter with increment/decrement buttons\n- A feature cards grid\n- Clean typography and spacing using Tailwind"}],"timestamp":1773033690034}}
{"type":"message","id":"d19d6e83","parentId":"2f81ae4f","timestamp":"2026-03-09T05:23:46.755Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":" The user wants me to create a standalone HTML file with React components using CDN. Let me create a polished, modern React app that includes:\n\n1. React 18 via CDN\n2. ReactDOM 18 via CDN\n3. Babel standalone for JSX transformation\n4. Tailwind CSS via CDN\n5. A clean card-based layout with:\n   - Header/hero section with gradient\n   - Interactive counter with useState\n   - Feature cards grid\n   - Responsive design\n   - Good typography and spacing\n\nLet me create this file at `public/react-app.html`.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":" I'll create a polished standalone React app with all the features you requested. Let me build this:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"functions.write:0","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/job/public/react-app.html","content":"<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"en\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <meta name=\"description\" content=\"A modern React app built with Tailwind CSS\">\n    <title>React + Tailwind App</title>\n    \n    <!-- Tailwind CSS CDN -->\n    <script src=\"https://cdn.tailwindcss.com\"></script>\n    \n    <!-- React 18 CDN -->\n    <script crossorigin src=\"https://unpkg.com/react@18/umd/react.development.js\"></script>\n    <script crossorigin src=\"https://unpkg.com/react-dom@18/umd/react-dom.development.js\"></script>\n    \n    <!-- Babel Standalone for JSX -->\n    <script src=\"https://unpkg.com/@babel/standalone/babel.min.js\"></script>\n    \n    <!-- Tailwind Config for Custom Colors -->\n    <script>\n        tailwind.config = {\n            theme: {\n                extend: {\n                    colors: {\n                        primary: {\n                            50: '#eff6ff',\n                            100: '#dbeafe',\n                            500: '#3b82f6',\n                            600: '#2563eb',\n                            700: '#1d4ed8',\n                        }\n                    }\n                }\n            }\n        }\n    </script>\n</head>\n<body class=\"bg-gray-50 min-h-screen\">\n    <div id=\"root\"></div>\n    \n    <script type=\"text/babel\">\n        const { useState } = React;\n        \n        // Feature Card Component\n        function FeatureCard({ icon, title, description }) {\n            return (\n                <div className=\"bg-white rounded-xl p-6 shadow-sm border border-gray-100 hover:shadow-md transition-shadow duration-200\">\n                    <div className=\"w-12 h-12 bg-primary-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4\">\n                        <span className=\"text-2xl\">{icon}</span>\n                    </div>\n                    <h3 className=\"text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2\">{title}</h3>\n                    <p className=\"text-gray-600 text-sm leading-relaxed\">{description}</p>\n                </div>\n            );\n        }\n        \n        // Counter Component\n        function Counter() {\n            const [count, setCount] = useState(0);\n            \n            return (\n                <div className=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-100 max-w-md mx-auto\">\n                    <h2 className=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-6 text-center\">Interactive Counter</h2>\n                    \n                    <div className=\"flex items-center justify-center mb-6\">\n                        <span className=\"text-5xl font-bold text-primary-600\">{count}</span>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    <div className=\"flex gap-3 justify-center\">\n                        <button \n                            onClick={() => setCount(c => c - 1)}\n                            className=\"px-6 py-3 bg-gray-100 hover:bg-gray-200 text-gray-700 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-2\"\n                        >\n                            <svg className=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                                <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M20 12H4\" />\n                            </svg>\n                            Decrement\n                        </button>\n                        \n                        <button \n                            onClick={() => setCount(0)}\n                            className=\"px-6 py-3 bg-gray-200 hover:bg-gray-300 text-gray-700 rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors duration-200\"\n                        >\n                            Reset\n                        </button>\n                        \n                        <button \n                            onClick={() => setCount(c => c + 1)}\n                            className=\"px-6 py-3 bg-primary-600 hover:bg-primary-700 text-white rounded-lg font-medium transition-colors duration-200 flex items-center gap-2\"\n                        >\n                            Increment\n                            <svg className=\"w-4 h-4\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                                <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M12 4v16m8-8H4\" />\n                            </svg>\n                        </button>\n                    </div>\n                    \n                    {count > 0 && (\n                        <p className=\"text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4\">\n                            You've clicked {count} time{count !== 1 ? 's' : ''}! 🎉\n                        </p>\n                    )}\n                </div>\n            );\n        }\n        \n        // Features Data\n        const features = [\n            {\n                icon: \"⚡\",\n                title: \"Lightning Fast\",\n                description: \"Built with performance in mind. React's virtual DOM ensures minimal updates and maximum speed.\"\n            },\n            {\n                icon: \"🎨\",\n                title: \"Beautiful Design\",\n                description: \"Styled with Tailwind CSS for a modern, responsive look that works on any device.\"\n            },\n            {\n                icon: \"📱\",\n                title: \"Fully Responsive\",\n                description: \"Mobile-first design approach ensures a great experience on phones, tablets, and desktops.\"\n            },\n            {\n                icon: \"🔧\",\n                title: \"Easy to Customize\",\n                description: \"Component-based architecture makes it simple to modify and extend functionality.\"\n            },\n            {\n                icon: \"🚀\",\n                title: \"Production Ready\",\n                description: \"Clean code structure following React best practices for scalable applications.\"\n            },\n            {\n                icon: \"💎\",\n                title: \"Modern Stack\",\n                description: \"Leveraging React 18 features and Tailwind's utility-first CSS for rapid development.\"\n            }\n        ];\n        \n        // Main App Component\n        function App() {\n            return (\n                <div className=\"min-h-screen\">\n                    {/* Hero Section */}\n                    <header className=\"bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-600 via-primary-700 to-indigo-800 text-white\">\n                        <div className=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 sm:py-24\">\n                            <div className=\"text-center\">\n                                <div className=\"inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-4 py-2 bg-white/10 rounded-full text-sm font-medium mb-6 backdrop-blur-sm\">\n                                    <span className=\"w-2 h-2 bg-green-400 rounded-full animate-pulse\"></span>\n                                    React 18 + Tailwind CSS\n                                </div>\n                                \n                                <h1 className=\"text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6\">\n                                    Build Something\n                                    <span className=\"block text-primary-100\">Amazing Today</span>\n                                </h1>\n                                \n                                <p className=\"text-lg sm:text-xl text-primary-100 max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed\">\n                                    A modern React application demonstrating state management, component composition, \n                                    and responsive design with Tailwind CSS.\n                                </p>\n                                \n                                <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\">\n                                    <button className=\"px-8 py-4 bg-white text-primary-700 rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-gray-50 transition-colors duration-200 shadow-lg\">\n                                        Get Started\n                                    </button>\n                                    <button className=\"px-8 py-4 bg-primary-500/50 text-white rounded-xl font-semibold hover:bg-primary-500/70 transition-colors duration-200 backdrop-blur-sm border border-white/20\">\n                                        Learn More\n                                    </button>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </header>\n                    \n                    {/* Counter Section */}\n                    <section className=\"py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n                        <div className=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\">\n                            <div className=\"text-center mb-12\">\n                                <h2 className=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">State Management Demo</h2>\n                                <p className=\"text-gray-600 max-w-xl mx-auto\">\n                                    Experience React's useState hook in action with this interactive counter component.\n                                </p>\n                            </div>\n                            <Counter />\n                        </div>\n                    </section>\n                    \n                    {/* Features Grid */}\n                    <section className=\"py-16 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 bg-white\">\n                        <div className=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\">\n                            <div className=\"text-center mb-16\">\n                                <h2 className=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">Features & Capabilities</h2>\n                                <p className=\"text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">\n                                    Everything you need to build modern web applications, bundled in a clean and intuitive package.\n                                </p>\n                            </div>\n                            \n                            <div className=\"grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6\">\n                                {features.map((feature, index) => (\n                                    <FeatureCard key={index} {...feature} />\n                                ))}\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </section>\n                    \n                    {/* Footer */}\n                    <footer className=\"bg-gray-900 text-gray-400 py-12 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8\">\n                        <div className=\"max-w-6xl mx-auto\">\n                            <div className=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-between items-center gap-4\">\n                                <div className=\"flex items-center gap-2\">\n                                    <div className=\"w-8 h-8 bg-primary-600 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center\">\n                                        <svg className=\"w-5 h-5 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\">\n                                            <path strokeLinecap=\"round\" strokeLinejoin=\"round\" strokeWidth={2} d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\" />\n                                        </svg>\n                                    </div>\n                                    <span className=\"font-semibold text-white\">ReactApp</span>\n                                </div>\n                                \n                                <p className=\"text-sm\">\n                                    Built with React 18, Tailwind CSS & Babel • No build step required\n                                </p>\n                                \n                                <div className=\"flex gap-6\">\n                                    <a href=\"#\" className=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">GitHub</a>\n                                    <a href=\"#\" className=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Docs</a>\n                                    <a href=\"#\" className=\"hover:text-white transition-colors\">Twitter</a>\n                                </div>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </footer>\n                </div>\n            );\n        }\n        \n        // Render the App\n        const root = ReactDOM.createRoot(document.getElementById('root'));\n        root.render(<App />);\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom","model":"moonshotai/kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":5309,"output":2968,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":8277,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1773033690036}}
